Solution 1

..[a....b]..
[c.......d].
a - c = +ve
b - d = -ve

[a.......b].
..[c....d]..
a - c = -ve
b - d = +ve

..[a.......b]
[c.......d]..
a - c = +ve
b - d = +ve

[a.......b]..
..[c.......d]
a - c = -ve
b - d = -ve

condition = (a-c)*(b-d) <= 0


Solution 2
..[a....b]...........
..........[c.......d]
b - c = -ve

..........[a.......b]
..[c....d]...........
a - d = +ve

condition = not(((a-d) > 0)||((b-c) < 0))
